Perry Fenwick https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perry_Fenwick 0 Perry Fenwick (born 29 May 1962) is an English film and television actor who currently plays Billy Mitchell in the BBC soap opera EastEnders, a role which he has played since 1998.
